\frac{2x^2}{2x} = x
\frac{2x^2 + 3x - 6}{2x+1} \approx  \frac{2x^2 (1 + 3/(2x))}{2x (1 + 1/(2x))} \approx x \left(1 + \frac{3}{2x}\right) \left(1 - \frac{1}{2x} \right) \approx x \left(1 + \frac{3/2 - 1/2}{x}\right) = x + 1
